    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the<strong> pork loin steak[s] </strong>dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rub with a little <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season both sides with <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>seasoned steak[s] </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until they're browned and cooked through</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
