    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water </strong>all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under cold running water until it’s cool, then squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can</p>",
