    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ground paprika </strong>and<strong> tomato paste</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688740315920-x200.jpg",
