      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, return the <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Stir through the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and crush the potatoes lightly with a fork – these are your <strong>spinach crushed potatoes</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>rested steak[s] </strong>finely</p>",
