    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the <strong>paprikash sauce </strong>with the <strong>sliced steak</strong> – this is your <strong>Hungarian-style pork paprikash</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>spinach crushed potatoes </strong>to the side</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
